msgid "Some Issues and Questions"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../doc/en/faq.rst:6
msgid ""
"This FAQ is here only mostly for historic reasons.  Checkout `pytest Q&A at "
"Stackoverflow <http://stackoverflow.com/search?q=pytest>`_ for many "
"questions and answers related to pytest and/or use :ref:`contact channels` "
"to get help."
